videos.headline: Bell breaks through for SDSU TD
videos.description: Chance Bell punches it into the end zone from five yards out to give SDSU a 14-0 lead over UNLV.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bell breaks through for SDSU TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bell runs up the middle for 19-yard Aztecs' TD
videos.description: Greg Bell bursts into the end zone for a 19-yard touchdown as San Diego State beats UNLV 34-6.
